This c++11 code sample completes my blog article at http://www.kakesa.net/programmation/cplusplus11-decouverte-de-ce-nouveau-dialecte/797.
This code is tested on Ubuntu GNU/Linux 11.10 with g++ 4.6.1.

Build the code in "build/bin" directory by typing : 

  make

Make a tar archive in "build" directory by typing :

  make tar
